              | Choose Service Type
            option [value="Door To Door"]
              | Door To Door
            option [value="Nodal"]
              | Nodal

        .col-md-4.margin-top
          label.site_labels for="billingModel"
            | Billing Model
          select.form-control.billingModel#billingModel_1[data-vehicleNumber="1"]
